"Rural Free Delivery was an idea as just as it was grand, and as welcome as it was necessary.",1,0,0,0,0,0
"The good work began October 1, 1896.",0,0,0,0,0,0
"The purpose of rural free delivery is to accommodate dwellers in the country, whether farmers or not.",0,0,0,0,0,0
