RAILROAD BONDS Every railroad in the country has been built and equipped by the sale of its bonds.,1,0,0,0,0,0
"In such cases amounts of stock of the same, or approximately the face value of the bond, have been given to the purchaser as a bonus or inducement.",0,0,0,0,0,0
"Of course, the controlling stock is always retained by the promoters; and it is through the representation of this stock that all the business of the corporation is carried on.",1,0,0,0,0,0
